remarks.format: ## Remarks 此类包含与 关联的 对象的集合。This class contains a collection of objects associated with a . 实例将其数据存储在磁盘范围的集合中，这些范围由 实例表示。A instance stores its data in a collection of disk extents, represented by instances. 特定的 与一个 相关联，同一 中的 对象具有相同的大小。A particular is associated with one , and objects in the same are of identical size. 将以范围增量的形式在 实例中添加和移除空间。Space is added to and removed from a instance in extent increments. 虽然 对象在磁盘上以文件的形式表示，但不应像普通文件那样移动或删除它们。Although objects are represented on disk as files, they should not be moved or deleted as normal files. 相反，应使用此类提供的方法直接添加和删除 实例。Rather, you should use the methods provided by this class for adding and deleting instances directly. 当范围不再包含任何活动数据时，通常会将其移除。Extents are usually removed when they no longer contain any active data. 但是，如果 `force` 方法中的 参数为 `true`，并且无法立即移除范围，则会引发异常。However, if the `force` parameter in the method is `true`, an exception is thrown if they cannot be removed immediately. 无法移除 中的最后一个范围，这意味着在添加范围后 属性不能为零。You cannot remove the last extent in the , which means that the property cannot be zero after an extent is added. ## Examples 此示例演示如何使用 和 类来添加和模拟日志序列中的范围。This example shows how to use the and classes to add and emulate extents in a log sequence.
